These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
There 7 different types of food: garlic, nectarine, corn, lemon, raspberry, banana, lettuce
 1. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5
 2. the person eating lemon is somewhere between the person eating banana and the person eating raspberry##7
 3. the person eating nectarine is somewhere between the person eating banana and the person eating garlic##7
 4. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the left of the person eating corn##5
 5. the person eating lettuce is not to the left of the person eating banana##8
 6. the person eating nectarine is in an odd position##4
 7. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
 8. the person eating banana is somewhere between the person eating raspberry and the person eating lettuce##7
 9. the person eating corn is not to the right of the person eating lemon##8
10. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| Food   | raspberry | garlic | nectarine | corn | lemon | banana | lettuce |

