.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, iced-tea, 7up, juice, tea, sprite
 1. the person drinking tea is the person drinking tea##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
 4. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 6. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the person drinking water##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| Beverage   | 7up | fanta | tea | sprite | iced-tea | water | juice |

